# <%= @current_collective.private_workspace? ? "Workspace" : "Collective" %> Settings

<% if @current_collective.archived? && @current_tenant.feature_enabled?("stripe_billing") %>
<% if @current_collective.created_by_id && @current_user.id == @current_collective.created_by_id %>
**Status: Inactive** — This collective is deactivated and not being billed. [Manage on billing page](/billing)
<% else %>
**Status: Inactive** — This collective is deactivated and not being billed. Only the collective creator can reactivate it.
<% end %>

<% else %>
Current settings for **<%= @current_collective.name %>**:

| Setting | Value |
|---------|-------|
| Name | <%= @current_collective.name %> |
| Handle | <%= @current_collective.handle %> |
| Description | <%= @current_collective.description || "(none)" %> |
| Timezone | <%= @current_collective.timezone %> |
| Tempo | <%= @current_collective.tempo %> |
| Synchronization Mode | <%= @current_collective.synchronization_mode %> |
<% unless @current_collective.private_workspace? %>
| Invitations | <%= @current_collective.all_members_can_invite? ? 'All members can invite' : 'Only admins can invite' %> |
| Representation | <%= @current_collective.any_member_can_represent? ? 'Any member can represent' : 'Only representatives' %> |
<% end %>
<% available_flags = FeatureFlagService.all_flags.select { |f| FeatureFlagService.tenant_enabled?(@current_tenant, f) && FeatureFlagService.flag_metadata(f).fetch("collective_level", false) } %>
<% if available_flags.any? %>

## Features Enabled

| Feature | Enabled |
|---------|---------|
<% available_flags.each do |flag_name| %>
<% metadata = FeatureFlagService.flag_metadata(flag_name) %>
<% collective_enabled_locally = @current_collective.feature_flag_enabled_locally?(flag_name) %>
| <%= metadata['name'] %> | <%= collective_enabled_locally ? 'Yes' : 'No' %> |
<% end %>
<% end %>
<% if @current_collective.feature_enabled?('api') && !@current_collective.private_workspace? && @collective_ai_agents.present? %>

## AI Agents in this Collective

<% @collective_ai_agents.each do |ai_agent| %>
* [<%= ai_agent.display_name %>](<%= ai_agent.path %>) - managed by <%= ai_agent.parent ? "[#{ai_agent.parent.display_name}](#{ai_agent.parent.path})" : "Unknown" %>
<% end %>
<% end %>

<% if @current_tenant.feature_enabled?("stripe_billing") && !@current_collective.is_main_collective? %>
<% if @current_collective.billing_exempt? %>
This collective is billing-exempt. [View billing](/billing)
<% else %>
This collective costs $3/month. [Manage billing](/billing)
<% end %>
<% end %>

## Additional Settings

* [Manage Automations](<%= @current_collective.path %>/settings/automations) - Configure event-triggered actions, webhooks, and schedules
<% end %>
